        <item>
            <title>【現場評測】Sony INZONE Buds 電競藍牙耳機，香港售價 + USB 插頭駁 PS5、電腦、手機超低延遲</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/sony-inzone-buds/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-inzone-buds</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/sony-inzone-buds/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 11:31:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony INZONE Buds]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198689</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony INZONE Buds 今日在香港發佈，它是一個專門為電子遊戲而設的無線藍牙耳機。過往講到電競耳機，大家只會聯想到是頭戴式設計的大牛龜耳機，在夏天打機往往會出一身大汗，而今次 Sony 發佈的是他們首個真・無線入耳式電競耳機，無拘無束之餘，又可得到低延遲聲音傳送的優點。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Sony INZONE Buds 真・無線耳機，採用入耳式設計，基本上同大家聽歌用的藍牙耳機例如 WF-1000XM5 無異。而最大分別就是它附設了一個超薄的小型 USB 手指，插在 PlayStation 5、PC、智能手機的 USB-C 插口上，直接利用 2.4GHz 無線訊號來傳輸聲音訊號。特點是相對藍牙而言，2.4GHz 無線訊號可做到更低延遲，跟頭戴式耳機一樣做到低於 30ms 的延遲率，非常適合玩 FPS、TPS 遊戲。而且接駁方便，毋須配對，只要一插到手機／平板／電腦／遊戲機就可以聽到歌、打機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198700" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198701" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳機內置有無線降噪功能，可消除周遭噪音。收音方面，亦可用到 AI 降噪功能，消除外界噪音做到更清晰的語音通話。</p><p>而除了用 USB-C 手指之外，Sony INZONE Buds 支援了藍牙 LE Audio 與支援此功能的智能手機、裝置無線連接。目前支援藍牙 LE Audio 的手機有 Xperia 1 IV、Xperia 5 IV，連接到這些手機，就毋須用 USB-C 手指，都可擁有超低延遲的打機音響體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>如果是未有支援 LE Audio 的智能手機，你可嘗試插上 USB 手指到智能手機。例如 iPhone 15，小編就嘗試過插上手指後可直接收聽 iPhone 上的聲音。</p><p>小編就嘗試連接 PS5，只要把 USB-C 手指插進遊戲機，戴上耳機後就馬上聽到遊戲機聲音，完全毋須配對。試玩《Call of Duty: Vanguard》可聽到四方八面傳來的槍聲，在小型耳機上都可做到精準定位。將 USB-C 手指插到電腦，就可即時收聽電腦聲響。在電腦上你可配合 INZONE Hub 軟件使用，獲得 360 Spatial Sound for Gaming 環繞聲效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198706" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲USB-C 手指直接插上 PS5 主機</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>但大家也要留意 Sony INZONE Buds 不支援 Bluetooth 藍牙連接，在一些沒有 USB-C 支援的裝置如 iPhone 14 或以前的 iPhone，就要透過轉接器才可聽歌／打機。</p><p>價格：HK$1,590</p><p>發售日期：10 月 11 日</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198702" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>同場加映：Sony INZONE H5 電競無線耳機</h2><p>Sony INZONE H5 是最新款的中階電競無線耳機，價位只為 HK$1,190。耳機淨重僅為 260g，比之前 H7 的 325g 大為輕巧，但採用與 INZONE H7 同一樣的耳棉，確保長時間佩戴都同樣舒適。耳機同樣以 USB-A 手指連接 PS5、電腦，透過 2.4GHz 無線訊號傳輸音訊，可做到極低的延遲。耳機充滿電後最多可用到 28 小時，就算耳機無電，只要快速充電 10 分鐘可獲得 3 小時的續航力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198707" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198709" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳機機身設有 Game/Chat Balance 撥桿，可直接控制遊戲／聊天聲量的平衡，確保你隊友的聲音不會被遊戲聲遮蓋。耳機也支援了 3.5mm 有線連接，就算耳機無電，都可馬上駁線到電腦。</p><p>價格：HK$1,190</p><p>發售日期：10 月 11 日</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2-768x519.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2.jpg 1143w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>同場加映：Sony ECM-S1 無線咪高風</h2><p>今日 Sony ECM-S1 無線咪高風出現在銅鑼灣 Sony 門市。這支咪高風可無線連接到你的 Sony 相機，適合串流直播用家使用。麥克風機身小巧輕便，配備三個 14 毫米大直徑麥克風元件，可捕捉自然人聲。音訊透過無線連接直接收錄到攝影機，在直播過程中不會出現聲音和影像分開輸入時有機會出現的「聲音和影像延遲」問題。</p><p>價格：HK$2,990</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
