        <item>
            <title>iOS 17.1 新功能避免誤按「動作按鈕」　防止 iPhone 15 在褲袋中誤開電筒、相機　</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/ios-17-1-prevent-action-button-press-unintentionally/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios-17-1-prevent-action-button-press-unintentionally</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/ios-17-1-prevent-action-button-press-unintentionally/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:37:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Action Button]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[動作按鈕]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198608</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPhone 15 Pro 系列將舊有的靜音撥桿變成了一個叫「動作按鈕」的多功能按鈕。用家可自訂不同功能到此按鈕，除靜音外，亦可設置長按啟動相機、電筒等。不過有用家發現在褲袋內經常錯誤地按壓了這個按鈕，帶來不便。iOS 17.1 Beta 3 就開始引入一個全新功能，避免相關事件發生。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max.jpg 730w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>iPhone 15 Pro 系列開始引入的「動作按鈕」，可以自訂不同功能，例如相機、電筒、靜音、我專注模式、錄音、放大鏡、捷徑等，用户長按這個按鈕，就可直接啟動已設置好的功能。不過有用家表示，即使要長按「動作按鈕」才會觸發相關功能，但電話放入褲袋後仍然經常誤按這個「動作按鈕」，以致在褲袋內經常誤開相機、電筒，大量耗用手機電量。</p><p>在 iOS 17.1 Beta 3 中，將加入自動感應功能，如感應到 iPhone 被放在口袋裡，長按「動作按鈕」也不會觸發到用家當初設置的功能，如相機、電筒等。</p><p>但用户也要留意，新機制只能防止「動作按鈕」被誤按。開啟了畫面，在鎖機畫面上的相機、電筒按鈕，目前仍沒有方法防止誤按。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53-382x580.jpg" alt="" width="382" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53-382x580.jpg 382w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53-593x900.jpg 593w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53-768x1165.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53-1012x1536.jpg 1012w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-11-16.49.53.jpg 1036w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 382px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/10/10/ios-17-1-action-button-tweak/">MacRumors</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
